-ready-to-launch-a-premium-hifi-audio-tier-123847826.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/spotify-may-finally-be-ready-to-launch-a-premium-hifi-audio-tier-123847826.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 43c29419-feb8-479f-a1a7-e402d322ced2</guid><dc:creator>史蒂夫登特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>Engadget</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder> Engadget</dc:rightsholder><pubDate> Tue, 20 Jun 2023 12:38:47 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687269445</ingested><modified> 2023-06-20T13:57:28+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Steve Dent]]></category><media:content height="5760" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-01/2d16d400-a0bc-11ed-bbff-b99ab14d0346" width="8640"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="5760" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-01/2d16d400-a0bc-11ed-bbff-b99ab14d0346" width="8640"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[John Nacion/STAR MAX/IPx]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Photo by: John Nacion/STAR MAX/IPx 2023 1/27/23 Spotify NYC Headquarters entrance with Spotify logo at 4 World Trade Center in Lower Manhattan, New York. Spotify to cut 6% of its global workforce as the music streaming company contends with a gloomy economic environment that has seen consumers and advertisers 